title: What will my phone display when one card is being used for a call and the other receives a call?
answer:
The CHM-U01/CHC-U01/CHC-U23 is a dual card single pass mobile phone. So when one card is being used for a call and the other receives a call, a voice notification will be displayed telling the calling party that your phone cannot be reached for the moment. 

 [This question is not applicable to the CHC-U03, which is a single SIM card phone.]()
